0Diplomat.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3ENetflix%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22584fa967-ca6b-4e23-a516-7caf1ab356f2%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20major%20death%20in%20the%20season%20finale%20throws%20Grace%20and%20Kate%20into%20chaos%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EKate%20learns%20that%20the%20aircraft%20carrier%20attack%2C%20which%20was%20executed%20by%20a%20Russian%20mercenary%2C%20was%20a%20false%20flag.%20Right-wing%20figure%20Margaret%20Roylin%20confesses%20to%20Tory%20Prime%20Minister%20Nicolas%20Trowbridge%2C%20whom%20she%20previously%20advised%2C%20that%20she%20orchestrated%20the%20entire%20incident%20to%20help%20the%20United%20Kingdom%20rally%20behind%20Trowbridge%20%E2%80%94%20and%20specifically%2C%20to%20prevent%20Scottish%20succession.%20The%20attack%2C%20however%2C%20was%20much%20more%20severe%20than%20intended%2C%20killing%20British%20sailors%20in%20the%20process%2C%20and%20Trowbridge%20reacts%20with%20abject%20fury%20and%20attempts%20to%20choke%20Roylin%20with%20his%20own%20hands.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Kate%20warms%20to%20Grace%20Penn%2C%20the%20vice%20president%2C%20after%20she%20arrives%20in%20London.%20After%20seeing%20Grace%20interact%20with%20Trowbridge%2C%20Kate%20decides%20to%20stop%20pursuing%20the%20vice%20presidency%2C%20and%20moves%20to%20recommend%20that%20Grace%20stay%20in%20office.%20Her%20husband%20Hal%20stops%20her%20from%20doing%20so%2C%20and%20delivers%20a%20devastating%20bit%20of%20information%3A%20Roylin%20didn't%20mastermind%20the%20attack%20on%20the%20aircraft%20carrier%20%E2%80%94%20Grace%20Penn%20did.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20season%20finale%2C%20Kate%20signals%20to%20Grace%20that%20she's%20aware%20of%20her%20involvement%20in%20the%20incident.%20In%20turn%2C%20Grace%20explains%20that%20she%20had%20no%20other%20choice.%20Like%20Roylin%2C%20she%20wished%20to%20prevent%20Scottish%20secession%2C%20but%20not%20for%20the%20same%20reasons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EScotland%2C%20Grace%20explains%2C%20is%20home%20to%20the%20United%20Kingdom's%20nuclear%20weapons%2C%20and%20houses%20the%20only%20place%20in%20Europe%20where%20the%20United%20States%20can%20dock%20its%20own%20nuclear%20submarines.%20That%20base%2C%20Creegan%2C%20would%20be%20the%20first%20European%20targets%20in%20a%20nuclear%20war%20with%20Russia%2C%20Grace%20explains%2C%20and%20should%20Scotland%20secede%20the%20country%20would%20be%20quick%20to%20close%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKate%20understands%20Grace's%20rationale%2C%20but%20makes%20the%20decision%20to%20report%20her%20actions%20to%20the%20State%20Department.%20She%20enlists%20her%20husband%20Hal%20(Rufus%20Sewell)%20to%20tell%20the%20secretary%20of%20state%20on%20her%20behalf%2C%20so%20that%20her%20record%20is%20clean%20when%20she%20steps%20into%20the%20vice%20presidency.%20As%20Kate%20assures%20Grace%20that%20she%20won't%20tell%20anyone%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0and%20that%20she's%20stopped%20pursuing%20the%20VP%20job%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0Hal%20goes%20rogue%20and%20skips%20over%20the%20secretary%20of%20state%20to%20go%20straight%20to%20President%20William%20Rayburn.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20backfires%20spectacularly%2C%20because%20Hal's%20revelation%20is%20so%20uniquely%20upsetting%20that%20it%20causes%20the%20elderly%20president%20to%20die%20on%20the%20spot.%20Hal%20barely%20manages%20to%20give%20Kate%20the%20heads%20up%20over%20the%20phone%20before%20secret%20service%20members%20rush%20onto%20the%20lawn%20to%20collect%20Grace%2C%20the%20new%20president%20of%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20got%20chills%20and%20I%20threw%20the%20script%20across%20the%20room%20and%20I%20was%20like%2C%20'What%20the%20fuck%3F'%26quot%3B%20Janney%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vanityfair.com%2Fhollywood%2Fstory%2Fallison-janney-the-diplomat-season-2-exclusive-awards-insider%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVanity%20Fair%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20ending.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20the%20best%20moment%20I've%20ever%20had%20reading%20a%20script.%26quot%3B%3C%