fe%20other%20than%20just%20acting%2C%26quot%3B%20Lillard%20said.%20That%20in%20turn%20led%20him%20to%20his%20latest%20venture.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a32247ca-58c3-4cff-9b71-9c6c74728bd4%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ELillard's%20liquor%20company%20Find%20Familiar%20Spirits%20is%20geared%20toward%20his%20favorite%20fandoms%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELillard's%20pivot%20into%20the%20spirits%20industry%20started%20about%20two%20years%20ago%2C%20when%20he%20cofounded%20his%20liquor%20company%20Find%20Familiar%20Spirits%2C%20which%20uses%20some%20of%20his%20favorite%20fandoms%20as%20inspiration%20for%20high-end%20liquor%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20avid%20tabletop%20gamer%2C%20Lillard%20made%20his%20first%20launch%2C%20Quest's%20End%2C%20a%20line%20of%20whiskeys%20inspired%20by%20Dungeons%20%26amp%3B%20Dragons.%20The%20company's%20second%20brand%2C%20Macabre%20Spirits%2C%20launched%20this%20month%20with%20a%20tequila%20reposado%20geared%20toward%20another%20community%20near%20and%20dear%20to%20Lillard's%20heart%3A%20horror%20fans.%20He%20even%20teamed%20with%20%26quot%3BThe%20Haunting%20of%20Hill%20House%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BMidnight%20Mass%26quot%3B%20creator%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmike-flanagan-netflix-shows-ranked%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMike%20Flanagan%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20launch%3B%20each%20bottle%20of%20Macabre%20comes%20with%20a%20horror%20novella%20written%20by%20Flanagan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20an%20homage%20and%20a%20love%20letter%20to%20sort%20of%20a%20gothic%20sense%20of%20storytelling%2C%26quot%3B%20Lillard%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELillard's%20collaboration%20with%20Flanagan%20has%20been%20fruitful%20on%20multiple%20levels.%20Just%20as%20Flanagan%20popped%20up%20in%20Lillard's%20liquor%20project%2C%20Lillard%20will%20soon%20play%20a%20small%20but%20significant%20role%20in%20one%20of%20Flanagan's%20movies%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Life%20of%20Chuck.%26quot%3B%20The%20movie%2C%20wh