0HAMPSHIRE%3A%20The%20witch%20of%20Hampton%2C%20Goody%20Cole%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224704%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22witch%20candles%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5cd1ed3b93a15208f67c5234%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223528%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHer%20real%20name%20was%20Eunice%20Cole.%3Cp%3EBUNDITINAY%2FShutterstock%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEunice%20%26quot%3BGoody%26quot%3B%20Cole%20was%20the%20only%20woman%20in%20New%20Hampshire%20history%20to%20be%20tried%20for%20witchcraft%20%E2%80%94%20multiple%20times.%20Her%20first%20charge%20was%20in%201656%2C%20and%20she%20was%20charged%20again%20in%201671%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hamptonhistoricalsociety.org%2Fgcole.htm%5C%22%3EHampton%20Historical%20Society.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20she%20died%20and%20her%20body%20was%20recovered%2C%20the%20townspeople%20were%20rumored%20to%20have%20staked%20her%20through%20the%20heart%20to%20prevent%20her%20from%20haunting%20their%20town%2C%20according%20to%20Atlas%20Obscura.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20continue%20to%20blame%20Goody%20Cole%20for%20the%20misfortunes%20of%20Hampton%20citizens%20for%20the%20past%20300%20years.%20For%20example%2C%20a%20boat%20full%20of%20Hampton%20residents%20overturned%2C%20and%20everyone%20on%20board%20drowned%2C%20even%20though%20they%20were%20within%20swimming%20distance%20of%20shore.%20People%20blamed%20Goody%20Cole%20for%20the%20crash%20and%20for%20cursing%20the%20passengers%20by%20having%20them%20forget%20how%20to%20swim.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ENEW%20JERSEY%3A%20The%20Jersey%20Devil%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221549%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22jersey%20devil%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5f402aa489aff80028ab74bb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221161%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20well-known%20rendering%20of%20the%20creature.%3Cp%3EBettman%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffig