e%20haunted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20tragic%20story%20supposedly%20took%20place%20there%2C%20where%20a%20boy%20was%20cornered%20by%20a%20group%20of%20bullies%20in%20the%20bathroom%20and%20shoved%20into%20a%20mirror%2C%20which%20shattered%20and%20killed%20him.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20avoid%20getting%20caught%20committing%20murder%2C%20the%20bullies%20decided%20to%20bury%20the%20body%20underneath%20the%20floorboards.%20Today%2C%20people%20say%20that%20if%20you%20go%20inside%20the%20school%2C%20you%20can%20see%20the%20reflection%20of%20the%20boy%20if%20you%20look%20in%20the%20mirror.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ETEXAS%3A%20The%20Candy%20Lady%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22902%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22winter%20olympics%202018%20south%20korea%20abandoned%20ski%20resort%20photos%2014%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5f40339042f43f001ddfe767%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22676%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECandy%20started%20appearing%20on%20windowsills.%3Cp%3EKim%20Hong-Ji%2FReuters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Urban%20Legends%20Online%2C%20in%20the%20early%201900s%2C%20children%20in%20an%20unnamed%20rural%20town%20in%20Texas%20started%20to%20disappear%2C%20and%20the%20residents%20blamed%20the%20Candy%20Lady.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20story%20says%20that%20she%20would%20go%20around%20leaving%20candy%20on%20children's%20windows%2C%20eventually%20luring%20the%20kids%20out%20with%20notes%20attached%2C%20promising%20more%20candy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20story%20picked%20up%20steam%20when%20a%20farmer%20reportedly%20found%20rotten%20teeth%20on%20his%20farm%20and%20later%20found%20the%20body%20of%20a%20boy%20with%20his%20pockets%20stuffed%20with%20candy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EUTAH%3A%20The%20curse%20of%20the%20Escalante%20Petrified%20Forest%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222222%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Escalante%20Petrified%20Forest%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5f40356b42f43f001ddfe771%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221666%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EEscalante%20Petrified%20Forest.%3Cp%3EIrinaK%2FShutterstock%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20it%20is%20illegal%20to%20take%20anything%20from%20Escalante%20Petrified%20Forest%20State%20Park%2C%20a%20legend%20says%20that%20anyone%20who%20takes%20pieces%20of%20petrified%20wood%20from%20the%20park%20will%20be%20cursed%20with%20bad%20luck%2C%20sickness%2C%20and%20accidents%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ksl.com%2Farticle%2F30052683%5C%22%3EKSL%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPark%20manager%20Kendall%20Farnsworth%20told%20KSL%20in%202014%20that%20he%20gets%20about%20a%20dozen%20packages%20every%20year%20containing%20a%20piece%20of%20wood%20from%20the%20park%20and%20an%20apologetic%20letter%20detailing%20the%20sender's%20misfortunes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EVERMONT%3A%20The%20frozen%20people%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22vermont%20forest%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5f4036ec42f43f001ddfe77a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221875%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWinters%20in%20Vermont%20are%20brutal.%3Cp%3ENichole%20Houghton%2FShutterstock%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFirst%20appearing%20in%20a%20diary%20that%20was%20published%20in%20the%20late%201800s%2C%20the%20legend%20of%20the%20hibernating%20older%20people%20recounts%20the%20tale%20of%20a%20poor%20family%20outside%20Montpelier%20who%20couldn't%20afford%20to%20feed%20and%20clothe%20the%20oldest%20members%20of%20their%20family%2C%20so%20they%20froze%20the%20people%20and%20buried%20them%2C%20wrote%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vermonter.com%2Fvermonts-deep-frozen-folks%2F%5C%22%3EVermonter.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELegend%20has%20it%20that%20when%20spring%20rolled%20around%2C%20the%20elders%20thawed%20out%20and%20were%20just%20fine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EVIRGINIA%