Fi.insider.com%2F5f40372242f43f001ddfe77b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221961%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOne%20of%20the%20most%20famous%20Bigfoot%20sightings.%3Cp%3EBettmann%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBigfoot%20is%20an%20internationally%20recognizable%20name%2C%20and%20has%20been%20spotted%20all%20over%20the%20country.%20But%2C%20Bigfoot%20has%20been%20spotted%20the%20most%20in%20Washington%20state%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bfro.net%2FGDB%2F%5C%22%3Ean%20online%20database%3C%2Fa%3E%20compiling%20all%20Bigfoot%20sightings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBigfoot%20is%20essentially%20a%20gigantic%20ape-like%20creature%20who%20is%20either%20a%20ferocious%20beast%20who%20attacks%20loggers%20and%20hikers%2C%20or%20a%20gentle%20giant%20who%20wants%20to%20be%20left%20alone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEither%20way%2C%20there's%20something%20creepy%20about%20an%20undiscovered%20species%20of%20animal%20wandering%20around%20the%20Pacific%20Northwest%2C%20evading%20capture.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWEST%20VIRGINIA%3A%20Mothman%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221686%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22mothman%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5f40382389aff80028ab7523%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221265%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Mothman%20statue%20in%20Point%20Pleasant%2C%20West%20Virginia.%3Cp%3EJack%20R%20Perry%20Photography%2FShutterstock%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%201966%2C%20stories%20say%20that%20West%20Virginia%20was%20visited%20by%20an%20insectoid%20flying%20creature%20with%20bright%20red%20eyes%20who%20resembled%20both%20a%20moth%20and%20a%20man%2C%20according%20to%20Atlas%20Obscura.%20He%20was%20spotted%20flying%20around%20the%20town%20of%20Point%20Pleasant%2C%20along%20with%20shining%20lights%20and%20the%20equally%20conspiratorial%20Men%20in%20Black%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMothman's%20origins%20have%20been%20said%20to%20be%20supernatural%2C%20alien%2C%20or%20a%20government%20experiment%20gone%20wrong.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Point%20Pleasant%20has%20embraced%20the%20monster%2C%20erecting%20a%20statue%2C%20creating%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mothmanmuseum.com%2F%5C%22%3Ea%20museum%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20even%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mothmanfestival.com%2F%5C%22%3Ededicating%20a%20festival%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20him.%20In%202002%2C%20a%20film%20starring%20Richard%20Gere%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Mothman%20Prophecies%2C%26quot%3B%20was%20released.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWISCONSIN%3A%20Boy%20Scout%20Lane%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22841%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22road%20wisconsin%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5f403a2689aff80028ab7537%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22630%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20road%20is%20in%20Stevens%20Point%2C%20Wisconsin.%3Cp%3EMarissa%20English%2FShutterstock%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20story%20of%20what%20exactly%20happened%20at%20Boy%20Scout%20Lane%20varies%2C%20but%20they%20all%20end%20with%20the%20same%20conclusion%3A%20a%20group%20of%20Boy%20Scouts%20dead%20on%20the%20road.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20some%20stories%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fweb.archive.org%2Fweb%2F20070928065938%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmcdowellnews.com%2Fservlet%2FSatellite%3Fpagename%3DMMN%252FMGArticle%252FMMN_BasicArticle%26c%3DMGArticle%26cid%3D1149193354782%26path%3D%2521news%2521localnews%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMcDowell%20News%3C%2Fa%3E%20wrote%2C%20there%20was%20a%20bus%20crash%20with%20no%20survivors%2C%20or%20they%20were%20murdered%20by%20their%20bus%20driver%2C%20or%20they%20just%20mysteriously%20vanished%20into%20the%20woods%20one%20by%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVisitors%20have%20reported%20seeing%20a%20swinging%20body%20in%20the%20trees%2C%20feeling%20like%20they%20are%20being%20watched%2C%20and%20finding%20child-size%20handprints.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWYOMING%3A%20Devils%2