3A%20Study%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIf%20a%20monkey%20types%20randomly%20at%20a%20keyboard%20for%20long%20enough%2C%20it%20will%20eventually%20write%20the%20complete%20works%20of%20Shakespeare.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20thought%20experiment%20has%20long%20been%20used%20to%20express%20how%20an%20infinite%20amount%20of%20time%20makes%20something%20that%20is%20incredibly%20unlikely%20--%20but%20still%20technically%20possible%20--%20become%20probable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20two%20Australian%20mathematicians%20have%20deemed%20the%20old%20adage%20misleading%2C%20working%20out%20that%20even%20if%20all%20the%20chimpanzees%20in%20the%20world%20were%20given%20the%20entire%20lifespan%20of%20the%20universe%2C%20they%20would%20%26quot%3Balmost%20certainly%26quot%3B%20never%20pen%20the%20works%20of%20the%20bard.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%26quot%3Binfinite%20monkey%20theorem%26quot%3B%20has%20been%20around%20for%20more%20than%20a%20century%2C%20though%20its%20origin%20remains%20unclear.%20It%20is%20commonly%20attributed%20to%20either%20French%20mathematician%20Emile%20Borel%20or%20British%20anthropologist%20Thomas%20Huxley%2C%20and%20some%20even%20think%20the%20general%20idea%20dates%20back%20to%20Aristotle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20a%20light-hearted%20but%20peer-reviewed%20study%20published%20earlier%20this%20week%2C%20the%20two%20mathematicians%20set%20out%20to%20determine%20what%20happens%20if%20generous%20yet%20finite%20limits%20were%20placed%20on%20the%20monkey%20typists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20calculations%20were%20based%20on%20a%20monkey%20spending%20around%2030%20years%20typing%20one%20key%20a%20second%20at%20a%20keyboard%20with%2030%20keys%20--%20the%20letters%20of%20the%20English%20language%20plus%20some%20common%20punctuation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%26quot%3Bheat%20death%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20universe%20was%20assumed%20to%20take%20place%20in%20around%20a%20googol%20of%20years%20--%20that%20is%20a%20one%20followed%20by%20100%20zeroes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20more%20practical%20considerations%20--%20such%20as%20what%20the%20monkeys%20would%20eat%2C%20or%20how%20they%20would%20survive%20the%20Sun%20engulfing%20Earth%20in%20a%20few%20billion%20years%20--%20were%20set%20aside.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMonkey%20labour%20falls%20short%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20only%20around%20a%20five%20percent%20chance%20that%20a%20single%20monkey%20would%20randomly%20write%20the%20word%20%26quot%3Bbanana%26quot%3B%20in%20their%20lifetime%2C%20according%20to%20the%20study%20in%20the%20journal%20Franklin%20Open.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShakespeare's%20canon%20includes%20884%2C647%20words%20--%20none%20of%20them%20banana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20broaden%20out%20the%20experiment%2C%20the%20mathematicians%20turned%20to%20chimpanzees%2C%20the%20closest%20relative%20of%20humans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20currently%20around%20200%2C000%20chimps%20on%20Earth%2C%20and%20the%20study%20presumed%20this%20population%20would%20remain%20stable%20until%20the%20end%20of%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20this%20massive%20monkey%20workforce%20fell%20very%2C%20very%20short.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20even%20like%20one%20in%20a%20million%2C%26quot%3B%20study%20co-author%20Stephen%20Woodcock%20of%20the%20University%20of%20Technology%20Sydney%20told%20New%20Scientist.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20every%20atom%20in%20the%20universe%20was%20a%20universe%20in%20itself%2C%20it%20still%20wouldn't%20happen.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20even%20if%20many%20more%20chimps%20who%20typed%20much%20quicker%20were%20added%20to%20the%20equation%2C%20it%20was%20still%20not%20plausible%20%26quot%3Bthat%20monkey%20labour%20will%20ever%20be%20a%20viable%20tool%20for%20developing%20written%20works%20of%20anything%20beyond%20the%20trivial%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20authors%20wrote%20in%20the%20study.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20study%20concluded%20by%20saying%20that%20Shakespeare%20himself%20may%20have%20inadvertently%20given%20an%20answer%20as%20to%20whether%20%26quot%3Bmonkey%20labour%20could%20meaningfully%20be%20a%20replacement%20for%20human%20endeavour%20as%20a%20source%20of%20scholarship%20or%20creativity%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20quote%20Hamlet%2C%20Act%203%2C%20Scene%203%2C%20Line%2087%3A%20'No'.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730381700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fqrtpmldg_baby-monkey-generic_625x300_28_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fnot-enough-time-in-universe-for-monkeys-to-pen-shakespeare-study-6915900%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%20thought%20experiment%20has%20long%20been%20used%20to%20express%20how%20an%20infinite%20amount%20of%20time%20makes%20something%20that%20is%20incredibly%20unlikely%20--%20but%20still%20technically%20possible%20--%20become%20probable.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fnot-enough-time-in-universe-for-monkeys-to-pen-shakespeare-study-6915900%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Who%20Will%20Lead%20MI%20After%20Retention%20Of%20Rohit%2C%20Pandya%2C%20SKY%3F%20Answer's%20Here%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFive-time%20IPL%20champions%20Mumbai%20Indians%20(MI)%20have%20retained%20their%20Indian%20core%20of%20the%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL)%202025.%20The%20franchise%20on%20Thursday%20announced%20the%20retention%20of%20five%20key%20players%2C%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Jasprit%20Bumrah%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1724-jasprit-bumrah-playerprofile%5C%22%3EJasprit%20Bumrah%3C%2Fa%3E%20(Rs%2018%20crore)%2C%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rohit%20Sharma%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayer