uad.%20He%20has%20just%20come%20here%20to%20prepare%20for%20the%20Australia%20tour%2C%20Abhishek%20(Nayar)%20made%20it%20clear%20yesterday.%20IPL%20retention%20has%20nothing%20to%20be%20spoken%20about%2C%20we%20have%20a%20Test%20match%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEveryone%20is%20available%20for%20selection%2C%20we%20will%20take%20a%20call%20tomorrow.%26quot%3B%20Gambhir%20admitted%20that%20the%20Test%20series%20defeat%20hurt%20the%20team%20but%20said%20it%20should%20spur%20the%20team%20to%20do%20better%20in%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20not%20going%20to%20sugarcoat%20that%20it%20is%20hurting.%20It%20should%20hurt%20and%20that%20will%20make%20us%20better.%20What%20is%20wrong%20in%20being%20in%20this%20position%3F%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20sure%20this%20will%20push%20the%20youngsters%20to%20be%20better%20cricketers.%20If%20we%20have%20results%20like%20Kanpur%2C%20might%20as%20well%20have%20results%20like%20this%20and%20keep%20moving%20forward%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Gambhir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20batters%20should%20be%20able%20to%20adapt%20to%20the%20situations%20of%20the%20game%20and%20perform%20accordingly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTest%20cricket%20should%20be%20played%20like%20Test%20cricket.%20If%20we%20have%20to%20get%20400%20runs%20inside%20a%20day's%20play%20we%20should%20be%20able%20to%20get%20it.%20For%20me%20it%20is%20about%20playing%20the%20sessions%20as%20well.%20If%20we%20play%204.5%20sessions%20we%20will%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20runs%20on%20board.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20complete%20cricketer%20is%20one%20who%20can%20adapt%20successfully.%20Not%20just%20being%20able%20to%20hit%20the%20stands%20but%20also%20rotate%20strike%20successfully%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20defensive%20technique%20of%20batters%20being%20impacted%20by%20T20%20cricket%2C%20Gambhir%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20more%20the%20T20%20cricket%20is%20played%20(around%20the%20world)%2C%20the%20more%20t