state's%20voters%20are%20concerned%20about%20immigration%20policies%2C%20a%20topic%20Trump%20has%20vehemently%20criticised%20Harris%20for.%20Abortion%20rights%20have%20also%20been%20a%20bone%20contention%2C%20as%20Republicans%20attempted%20to%20reinstate%20a%20nearly%20total%20ban%20on%20abortions.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EGeorgia%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnGeorgia%2C%20another%20state%20where%20Biden%20registered%20a%20victory%20by%20a%20slander%20margin%20of%2013%2C000%20votes%2C%20is%20not%20just%20a%20swing%20state%20but%20also%20a%20legal%20battlefield%20for%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20who%20faces%20allegations%20of%20election%20interference.%20The%20state%20is%20home%20to%20a%20diverse%20demographic%2C%20with%20a%20significant%20African-American%20population%20crucial%20to%20Democratic%20strategies.%20Harris's%20campaign%20aims%20to%20engage%20this%20demographic%20amid%20reports%20of%20growing%20disillusionment%20with%20the%20Biden%20administration.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EMichigan%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnIn%20Michigan%2C%20where%20Biden%20won%20by%201%2C50%2C000%20votes%2C%20the%20landscape%20is%20complicated%20by%20significant%20discontent%20among%20key%20voter%20groups.%20President%20Biden%20has%20faced%20criticism%20for%20his%20foreign%20policy%2C%20particularly%20on%20US%20military%20aid%20to%20Israel%2C%20which%20has%20bombarded%20Gaza%20for%20over%20a%20year.%20Michigan%20has%20the%20largest%20proportion%20of%20Arab-American%20residents%20in%20the%20US%2C%20and%20their%20support%20for%20Biden%20has%20become%20increasingly%20tenuous.%20Harris%20has%20shifted%20her%20tone%20vis-a-vis%20Israel%2C%20aiming%20to%20reassure%20voters%20who%20feel%20sidelined%20by%20the%20administration's%20policies%20while%20Trump%20keeps%20firm%20his%20stance%20on%20rapid%20military%20action.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3ENevada%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnNevada%2C%20traditionally%20a%20Democratic%20stronghold%2C%20shows%20signs%20of%20a%20tightening%20race%2C%20with%20recent%20polls%20suggesting%20a%20shift%20in%20favour%20of%20Republicans.%20Both%20campaigns%20are%20actively%20courting%20Nevada's%20substantial%20Latino%20population%2C%20crucial%20to%20any%20candidate's%20success%20in%20the%20state.%20The%20economic%20recovery%20post-COVID%20has%20been%20sluggish%20in%20Nevada%20compared%20to%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20country%2C%20making%20it%20a%20big%20concern.%20The%20high%20unemployment%20rate%20and%20cost-of-living%20pressures%20are%20also%20key%20issues%20for%20voters%20in%20this%20state.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3ENorth%20Carolina%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnIn%20North%20Carolina%2C%20Donald%20Trump's%20narrow%20victory%20margin%20in%202020%20(by%2074%2C000%20votes)%20has%20made%20this%20state%20a%20toss-up%20for%202024.%20With%20demographics%20and%20issues%20mirroring%20those%20of%20neighbouring%20Georgia%20and%20Arizona%2C%20both%20candidates%20are%20pouring%20resources%20into%20North%20Carolina.%20Trump%20recently%20held%20a%20rally%20here%2C%20promising%20to%20end%20inflation%2C%20stop%20the%20influx%20of%20criminals%20into%20the%20country%20and%20restore%20the%20American%20dream.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EPennsylvania%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnPennsylvania%20holds%2019%20electoral%20votes%20and%20is%20a%20critical%20target%20for%20both%20candidates.%20Biden's%20roots%20in%20Scranton%20give%20him%20a%20personal%20connection%20to%20voters%20in%20this%20working-class%20state.%20The%20economic%20landscape%20has%20shifted%20dramatically%20since%20Biden%20took%20office%2C%20with%20inflation%20affecting%20household%20budgets.%20Recent%20statistics%20show%20that%20grocery%20prices%20in%20Pennsylvania%20have%20risen%20faster%20than%20in%20any%20other%20state%2C%20leading%20to%20significant%20cost-of-living%20pressures%20among%20residents.%20Both%20campaigns%20are%20acutely%20aware%20that%20economic%20issues%20could%20sway%20undecided%20vot