%E2%80%99s%20in%20their%20food.%20Our%20mission%20is%20to%20educate%20and%20empower%20consumers.%E2%80%9D-%20Dr%20Aman%20Basheer%20Sheikh%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20journey%20has%20not%20been%20without%20challenges.%20Initially%2C%20the%20team%20envisioned%20sourcing%20data%20from%20existing%20databases%20but%20soon%20discovered%20a%20lack%20of%20centralised%20repositories%20for%20product%20information%20in%20India.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20thought%20it%20would%20be%20easy%20to%20access%20a%20comprehensive%20database%2C%20but%20that%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20the%20case%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ravi%20says.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20found%20that%20information%20on%20the%20internet%20was%20often%20inaccurate%20or%20outdated.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20attempting%20to%20scrape%20data%20for%20over%2050%2C000%20products%2C%20they%20opted%20for%20a%20meticulous%2C%20ground-up%20approach%20to%20ensure%20accuracy.%20Currently%2C%20the%20team%20sends%20photographers%20to%20supermarkets%20to%20capture%20product%20images%20and%20ingredient%20labels%20directly.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20only%20rely%20on%20internet%20data%20for%20about%2020%25%20of%20our%20information%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ravi%20clarifies.%20Essentially%2C%20they%20crowdsource%20product%20images%20and%20information%20to%20verify%20product%20details.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%227521127830%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECombating%20misleading%20labels%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETruthIn%E2%80%99s%20assessments%20extend%20beyond%20nutritional%20profiles.%20Their%20algorithm%20evaluates%20several%20factors%3A%2045%25%20is%20based%20on%20the%20nutritional%20profile%2C%2045%25%20on%20the%20health%20impact%20of%20ingredients%2C%20and%2010%25%20on%20the%20manufacturing%20process.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20adhere%20to%20ICMR%20and%20NIN%20standards%20set%20by%20dietitians%20and%20nutritionists%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ravi%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20algorithm%20interprets%20product%20images%2C%20extracting%20and%20manually%20verifying%20information%20before%20assigning%20a%20health%20rating.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20even%20penalise%20products%20for%20adding%20known%20harmful%20additives%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Aman%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnhealthy%20diets%2C%20alongside%20physical%20inactivity%2C%20tobacco%20and%20alcohol%20use%2C%20and%20air%20pollution%2C%20remain%20major%20contributors%20to%20non-communicable%20diseases%20(NCDs).%20A%20report%20by%20the%20Indian%20Council%20of%20Medical%20Research%20(ICMR)%20reveals%20that%20the%20proportion%20of%20deaths%20from%20non-communicable%20diseases%20(NCDs)%20in%20India%20rose%20significantly%2C%20from%2037.9%25%20in%201990%20to%2061.8%25%20in%202016%2C%20with%20cardiovascular%20diseases%2C%20chronic%20respiratory%20diseases%2C%20cancers%2C%20and%20diabetes%20being%20the%20leading%20causes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20these%20rising%20concerns%20that%20TruthIn%20hopes%20to%20address.%C2%A0%20%E2%80%9CIf%20we%20talk%20about%20potato%20chips%2C%20you%20might%20think%20they%E2%80%99re%20bad%20because%20they%E2%80%99re%20fried%20in%20oil%20and%20salt%2C%20but%20they%20often%20contain%20many%20other%20additives%20that%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20realise%20or%20understand%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Aman%20shares.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20these%20hurdles%2C%20the%20team%20remains%20committed%20to%20their%20goal.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20approach%20this%20from%20a%20solution-based%20perspective%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Aman%20says.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20problem%20is%20that%20people%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20what%E2%80%99s%20in%20their%20food.%20Our%20mission%20is%20to%20educate%20and%20empower%20consumers.%E2%80%9D%20The%20TruthIn%20team%20consists%20of%2035%20members%2C%20including%2015%20nutritionists%20and%20doctors%2C%20working%20alongside%20tech%20professionals.%20The%20initiative%20is%20entirely%20bootstrapped%20and%20self-funded.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20TruthIn%20has%20an%20active%20user%20base%20of%20approximately%2085%2C000%20to%201%2C00%2C000%20users%20each%20month.%20The%20app%20features%20a%20unique%20TruthIn%20Rating%20system%20that%20assigns%20health%20impact%20of%20food%20products.%20Products%20are%20assigned%20health%20ratings%20on%20a%20scale%20from%201%20to%205%2C%20with%205%20being%20the%20healthiest%20option.%20Users%20can%20easily%20find%20products%20that%20match%20their%20dietary%20needs%20and%20preferences%20through%20filter%20tags%20for%20nutrients%2C%20lifestyle%2C%20and%20allergens.%20The%20Shopping%20Cart%20Insights%20makes%20the%20shopping%20experience%20better%20by%20giving%20intelligent%20insights%20on%20cart%20contents%2C%20ensuring%20all%20products%20meet%20health%20criteria.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%224678180483%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20simply%20scanning%20the%20barcode%20on%20a%20product%E2%80%99s%20packaging%2C%20users%20can%20get%20detailed%20information%20about%20its%20rating%20and%20relevant%20tags%2C%20such%20as%20high%20sodium%2C%20fat%2C%20sugar%20content%2C%20cholesterol%20levels%2C%20and%20sources%20of%20fibre%20or%20protein.%20Additionally%2C%20TruthIn%20is%20building%20a%20depository%20of%20products%20for%20users%20to%20check%20specific%20product%20information%20without%20scanning.%20With%20a%20subscription%2C%20users%20can%20also%20get%20personalised%20dietary%20insights%20through%20the%20MatchMeter%20feature%2C%20which%20considers%20age%2C%20gender%2C%20health%20conditions%2C%20and%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20TruthIn%20announced%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F350012%2Frevant-himatsingka-food-pharmer-nutrition-ingredient-list-read-label-padhega-india-mumbai%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERevant%20Himatsingka%2C%20popular%20as%20Foodpharmer%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20as%20their%20brand%20ambassador.%20%E2%80%9CRevant%20and%20our%20journey%20kind%20of%20began%20at%20the%20same%20time.%20I%20was%20really%20impressed%20that%20one%20single%20person%20has%20the%20courage%20to%20do%20this%20so%20openly%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Aman%20shares.%20Together%2C%20they%20aim%20to%20tackle%20the%20challenges%20posed%20by%20complex%20product%20labels%20and%20health%20information%2C%20making%20it%20easier%20for%20users%20to%20make%20informed%20decisions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Arunava%20Banerjee%3B%20All%20images%20courtesy%20Dr%20Aman%20Basheer%20Sheikh%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730204449000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-10-29-at-1.58.28-PM-1_11zon-1730190690.jpeg%3Fw%3D1280%26quality%3D89%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D372834%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22TruthIn%2C%20an%20app%20co-founded%20by%20Ravi%20Teja%20Putrevu%2C%20Dr%20Aman%20Basheer%20Sheikh%2C%20and%20Raghav%20Putrevu%2C%20simplifies%20food%20labelling%20by%20providing%20instant%20health%20ratings%20through%20barcode%20scanning.%20Born%20from%20personal%20experience%20with%20acromegaly%2C%20the%20app%20empowers%20people%20to%20make%20informed%20dietary%20choices.%20With%2085%2C000%E2%80%93100%2C000%20monthly%20users%2C%20TruthIn%20aims%20to%20increase%20consumer%20awareness%20and%20promote%20healthier%20eating%20habits.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Hemlata%20Chouhan%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F372834%2Ftruthin-app-healthy-food-choices-scan-barcode-easy-food-labels-foodpharmer%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Paddy%20to%20Compost%20in%2020%20Days%3A%20How%20Merino%20Industries%E2%80%99%20Innovation%20Is%20Fighting%20Stubble%20Burning%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20has%20been%20published%20in%20partnership%20with%20Merino%20Industries%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20drive%20through%20the%20North%20Indian%20countryside%20at%20this%20time%20of%20the%20year%20promises%20to%20be%20beautiful.%20Acres%20upon%20acres%20of%20crops%2C%20their%20golden%20hues%20signifying%20a%20beautiful%20harvest%2C%20account%20for%20a%20major%20chunk%20of%20your%20view.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20a%20silent%20threat%20looms%20in%20the%20backdrop.%20Across%20agrarian%20units%20in%20Delhi%20and%20parts%20of%20the%20Indo-Gangetic%20plains%2C%20stubble%20burning%20in%20winter%20has%20proven%20to%20be%20a%20menace%20%E2%80%94%20one%20that%20ripples%20into%20an%20annual%20public%20health%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECome%20October%2C%20farmers%20busy%20themselves%20reaping%20the%20grain.%20What%E2%80%99s%20left%20behind%20are%20two-foot-high%20stubble%20stalks.%20With%20only%20a%20short%20window%20before%20the%20land%20is%20prepared%20for%20the%20next%20cropping%20season%2C%20setting%20fire%20to%20the%20field%20seems%20the%20only%20viable%20solution%20to%20do%20away%20with%20the%20stubble%20for%20most%20farmers.%20But%2C%20the%20burning%20does%20not%20come%20without%20adverse%20effects%20%E2%80%94%20both%2C%20on%20the%20nation%E2%80%99s%20air%20quality%20and%20its%20citizens%E2%80%99%20lungs%20while%20further%20deteriorating%20the%20quality%20of%20soil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20correlating%20air%20quality%20data%20with%20respiratory%20health%2C%20a%20study%20found%20that%20most%20farmers%20with%20compromised%20lung%20function%20were%20those%20who%20had%20been%20exposed%20to%20long%20hours%20of%20toxic%20haze.%20The%20plumes%20of%20smoke%20are%20a%20bed%20for%20gaseous%20pollutants%20%E2%80%94%20149.24%20million%20tonnes%20of%20carbon%20dioxide%20(CO2)%2C%20over%209%20million%20tonnes%20of%20carbon%20monoxide%20(CO)%2C%200.25%20million%20tonnes%20of%20oxides%20of%20sulphur%20(SOX)%2C%201.28%20million%20tonnes%20of%20particulate%20matter%2C%20and%200.07%20million%20tonnes%20of%20black%20carbon%2C%20to%20be%20precise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20a%20study%20probing%20the%20culprit%20for%20the%20dipping%20winter%20AQI%20(air%20quality%20index)%20of%20the%20Delhi-NCR%20region%20discovered%20that%20a%20statistically%20significant%20half%20of%20particulate%20matter%20is%20contributed%20by%20burning%20crop%20residues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201000px)%20100vw%2C%201000px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FMerino_11zon-1730200994.jpg%3Ffit%3D1200%252C628%26quality%3D89%26ssl%3D1%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Stubble%2C%20left%20behind%20from%20the%20harvest%2C%20proves%20to%20be%20a%20problem%20for%20farmers%20across%20North%20India%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FMerino_11zon-1730200994.jpg%3Fw%3D1200%26amp%3Bquality%3D89%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FMerino_11zon-1730200994.jpg%3Fresize%3D300%252C157%26amp%3Bquality%3D89%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FMerino_11zon-1730200994.jpg%3Fresize%3D500%252C262%26amp%3Bquality%3D89%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FMerino_11zon-1730200994.jpg%3Fresize%3D768%252C402%26amp%3Bquality%3D89%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FMerino_11zon-1730200994.jpg%3Fresize%3D150%252C79%26amp%3Bquality%3D89%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-372861%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EStubble%2C%20left%20behind%20from%20the%20harvest%2C%20proves%20to%20be%20a%20problem%20for%20farmers%20across%20North%20India.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOutlawing%20and%20incentivising%20stubble%20burning%20haven%E2%80%99t%20had%20the%20desired%20outcome.%20So%2C%20instead%20of%20punishing%20the%20process%2C%20can%20industries%20combat%20stubble%20burnings%20with%20advanced%20mechanisms%3F%20Merino%20Industries%2C%20one%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20largest%20manufacturers%20of%20decorative%20laminates%2C%20has%20an%20inventive%20take%20on%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20part%20of%20its%20commitment%20to%20environment%20and%20sustainability%2C%20under%20its%20programme%20named%20%E2%80%98Nirmal%E2%80%99%2C%20Merino%20Industries%20%E2%80%94%20in%20collaboration%20with%20VNIT%20Nagpur%20%E2%80%94%20has%20developed%20an%20innovative%20solution%20at%20Merino%20Innovation%20Center%20at%20VNIT%20Nagpur%20to%20overcome%20the%20stated%20challenges%20of%20stubble%20burning.%20In%20situ%2C%20rapid%20digestion%20of%20paddy%20straw%20is%20achieved%20through%20a%20patented%20microbial%20culture%20called%20%E2%80%98Bajarang%20Baan%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20converts%20paddy%20straw%20into%20nutrient-rich%20compost%20in%20about%2020%20days.%20The%20compost%20so%20produced%20meets%20FCO%20Standards.%20The%20solution%20so%20developed%20is%20in%20production%20use%20at%20Merino%20Hapur%20where%20approximately%202%20MT%20of%20paddy%20straw%20is%20converted%20per%20day%20into%20nutrient-rich%20compost%20and%20has%20also%20been%20deployed%20through%20CII%20at%20Sangrur%2C%20Barnala%2C%20and%20Sirsa.%20The%20entire%20operation%20is%20simple%20to%20carry%20out%20and%20is%20cost-effective%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mr%20Prakash%20Lohia%2C%20CMD%2C%20Merino%20Industries%2C%20shares.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhere%20there%20is%20smoke%2C%20there%20is%20fire%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NCR%20city%20routinely%20battles%20farm%20fires%20stemming%20from%20stubble%20burning%20every%20winter.%20The%20farmers%20are%20not%20without%20solutions%2C%20but%20they%20share%20a%20reluctance%20to%20shed%20old%20habits%20and%20transition%20to%20new%20ones.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20farmers%20blamed%20a%20stubborn%20mindset%20%E2%80%94%20%E2%80%9CWe%20don%E2%80%99t%20remember%20a%20time%20when%20we%20have%20not%20burned%20%5Bstubble%5D%20in%20our%2012%20acres%20of%20land.%20We%20know%20it%20destroys%20soil%20nutrients%20but%20it%20is%20not%20easy%20to%20change.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20one%20hand%2C%20stands%20India%E2%80%99s%20farming%20community%2C%20which%20struggles%20to%20deal%20with%20the%20side%20effects%20of%20ineffective%20disposal%20of%20paddy%20straw%20(to%20the%20tune%20of%2020%20MT%20per%20year)%2C%20while%20on%20the%20other%20are%20policymakers%20who%20are%20advocating%20for%20better%20air%20quality%20indices.%20Merino%20Industries%20promises%20a%20landmark%20solution%20to%20bridge%20the%20chasm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20over%20five%20decades%2C%20environmental%20protection%20has%20remained%20an%20inseparable%20part%20of%20their%20economic%20activity%20with%20their%20%E2%80%98Nirmal%E2%80%99%20programme%20addressing%20five%20pillars%20%E2%80%94%20Bh%C5%ABmih%20(soil)%2C%20Apah%20(water)%2C%20Analah%20(fire)%2C%20Vayu%20(air)%2C%20and%20Khang%20(space).%20The%20multinational%20recently%20claimed%20to%20have%20succeeded%20in%20meeting%20nearly%2075%20percent%20of%20its%20energy%20needs%20through%20renewable%20sources.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhen%20paddy%20straw%20becomes%20compost%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20agricultural%20statistics%2C%20Punjab%2C%20Haryana%2C%20NCR%20amid%20other%20North%20Indian%20areas%20are%20major%20rice%20producers%20in%20the%20country%2C%20generating%20approximately%2050%20million%20tonnes%20of%20paddy%20straw%20annually.%20Around%2088%20percent%20of%20the%20paddy%20straw%20is%20reportedly%20burnt%20in%20the%20fields.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERevealing%20how%20they%20are%20reinventing%20the%20wheel%20of%20dealing%20with%20stubble%2C%20Merino%20Industries%20points%20to%20their%20patented%20microbial%20culture%20%E2%80%98Bajarang%20Baan%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20converts%20paddy%20straw%20into%20nutrient-rich%20compost%20in%20about%2020%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDetailing%20the%20tactic%2C%20Mr%20Lohia%20shares%20the%20compost%20is%20prepared%20through%20an%20ingenious%20in-situ%20rapid%20digestion%20at%20the%20Merino%20Hapur%20plant.%20%E2%80%9CApproximately%202%20MT%20of%20paddy%20straw%20is%20converted%20per%20day%20into%20nutrient-rich%20compost%20and%20has%20also%20been%20deployed%20through%20CII%20at%20Sangrur%2C%20Barnala%2C%20and%20Sirsa.%20The%20entire%20operation%20is%20simple%20to%20carry%20out%20and%20is%20cost-effective.%20The%20process%20is%20devoid%20of%20any%20pretreatment%20other%20than%20straw%20size%20reduction%20and%20post-operation%20separation%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mr%20Lohia%20points%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201000px)%20100vw%2C%201000px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FMerino-1-1730201185.jpg%3Ffit%3D1200%252C628%26quality%3D89%26ssl%3D1%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Through%20an%20innovative%20technology%2C%20the%20paddy%20is%20converted%20into%20a%20nutrient-rich%20compost%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FMerino-1-1730201185.jpg%3Fw%3D1200%26amp%3Bquality%3D89%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FMerino-1-1730201185.jpg%3Fresize%3D300%252C157%26amp%3Bquality%3D89%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FMerino-1-1730201185.jpg%3Fresize%3D500%252C262%26amp%3Bquality%3D89%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FMerino-1-1730201185.jpg%3Fresize%3D768%252C402%26amp%3Bquality%3D89%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FMerino-1-1730201185.jpg%3Fresize%3D150%252C79%26amp%3Bquality%3D89%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-372863%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThrough%20an%20innovative%20technology%2C%20the%20paddy%20is%20converted%20into%20a%20nutrient-rich%20compost.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20a%20suitable%20alternative%20to%20avert%20stubble%20burning%20for%20more%20reasons%20than%20one.%20Mr%20Lohia%20shares%20the%20findings%20of%20a%20report%20that%20spotlighted%20the%20array%20of%20benefits%20that%20in-situ%20utilisation%20of%20paddy%20straw%20has%20in%20bringing%20the%20nutrients%20back%20to%20the%20soil%20%E2%80%94%20otherwise%20lost%20during%20burning%20or%20transporting%20the%20residues%20for%20use%20outside%20the%20farm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20confident%20that%20%E2%80%9Csuch%20practices%20and%20business%20models%20would%20also%20ensure%20economic%20growth%20for%20the%20farmers%20as%20well%20as%20a%20cleaner%20environment.%20This%20soil%20incorporation%20will%20have%20long-term%20benefits%20for%20improving%20the%20quality%20of%20soil%2C%20increasing%20water-use%20efficiency%2C%20and%20reducing%20the%20intensity%20of%20chemical%20fertilisers%20being%20used.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20doubt%2C%20the%20technology%20is%20innovative%2C%20boasting%20a%20quick%20and%20radical%20alternative%20to%20burning%20the%20stubble.%20While%20being%20in%20synergy%20with%20Merino%20Industries%E2%80%99%20commitment%20to%20the%20environment%2C%20the%20process%20utilises%20electricity%20only%20during%20the%20size%20reduction%20of%20paddy%20straw%20and%20the%20rendered%20compost%20also%20improves%20the%20quality%20of%20the%20soil%20it%20is%20added%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20proud%20to%20create%20%26amp%3B%20collaborate%20with%20VNIT%20at%20the%20Merino%20Innovation%20Center%20within%20the%20campus%2C%20which%20stands%20as%20a%20testament%20to%20how%20academia%20and%20industry%20can%20unite%20to%20create%20meaningful%2C%20problem-solving%20solutions.%20The%20encouraging%20results%20from%20our%20test%20beds%20give%20us%20confidence%20in%20expanding%20these%20practices%20across%20the%20farmlands%20in%20order%20to%20address%20critical%20air%20quality%20issues%20from%20stubble%20burning.%20This%20initiative%20aligns%20with%20Merino%E2%80%99s%20mission%20of%20promoting%20Universal%20Weal%20through%20trade%20and%20industry%2C%20contributing%20to%20both%20environmental%20and%20societal%20well-being%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Mr%20Lohia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESources%3C%2Fem%3E%3A%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcpcb.nic.in%2Fuploads%2FAQM%2FTERI_Brief_Report.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDoes%20air%20quality%20from%20crop%20residue%20burning%20in%20close%20proximity%20to%20residential%20areas%20adversely%20affect%20respiratory%20health%3F%20%3C%2Fa%3Eby%20Central%20Pollution%20Control%20Board%2C%20Published%20in%20October%202021.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%