0Initially%2C%20Dr.%20Sumitra%20managed%20all%20the%20calls%20and%20messages%20herself%2C%20offering%20the%20service%20for%20free.%20Soon%2C%20parents%20began%20sharing%20it%20with%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%224678180483%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20would%20get%20calls%20from%20all%20over%20the%20country%2C%20including%20remote%20villages%20from%20Rajasthan%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20and%20more.%20From%20250%20members%2C%20we%20grew%20to%20500%20over%20a%20few%20months.%20Soon%2C%20I%20was%20handling%20more%20than%201%2C000%20questions%20daily%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%20Gurugram%20resident.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20patient%20numbers%20increased%2C%20Dr%20Sumitra%20onboarded%20additional%20doctors%20to%20provide%20round-the-clock%20support.%20Babynama%20now%20has%2050%20paediatricians%20on%20board%20who%20offer%20chat%20support%20till%2011%20pm%20and%20call%20support%2024%2F7.%20She%20also%20started%20thinking%20of%20ways%20to%20reach%20more%20people%2C%20thus%20creating%20pages%20on%20Instagram%20and%20YouTube%20to%20educate%20parents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20help%20sustain%20the%20service%2C%20she%20eventually%20introduced%20a%20small%20consultation%20fee%20of%20Rs%20100%20per%20call.%20By%20March%202023%2C%20with%20over%201%2C000%20daily%20queries%20and%201%2C000%20members%2C%20Babynama%20expanded%20to%20a%20full-fledged%20website%20and%20application.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMaking%20paediatric%20care%20accessible%3A%20How%20Babynama%20works%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInitially%20offering%2024%2F7%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F366063%2Fnehal-shah-travel-with-kids-children-nature-trails-treks-experiences-toddlers-mumbai%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esupport%20for%20new%20parents%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Babynama%20has%20since%20added%20new%20programmes%20to%20meet%20the%20evolving%20needs%20of%20parents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMoms%20began%20asking%20questions%20about%20breastfeeding%2C%20starting%20solids%2C%20nutritious%20meals%2C%20and%20sleep.%20To%20solve%20these%20queries%2C%20we%20onboarded%20lactation%20experts%2C%20nutritionists%2C%20and%20sleep%20specialists%2C%20and%20created%20programmes%20around%20the%20same%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dr%20Sumitra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBabynama%E2%80%99s%20plans%20start%20at%20Rs%20499.%20The%20%3Cem%3EEssential%20Care%3C%2Fem%3E%20plan%2C%20priced%20at%20Rs%201%2C999%2C%20provides%20access%20to%20a%20WhatsApp%20group%20with%20paediatricians%2C%2024%2F7%20video%20consultations%2C%20and%20monthly%20milestone%20check-ups.%20Their%20%3Cem%3EHolistic%20Care%3C%2Fem%3E%20plan%2C%20which%20includes%20access%20to%20a%20dedicated%20paediatrician%20in%20a%20private%20group%20along%20with%20breastfeeding%20and%20nutrition%20support%2C%20is%20available%20for%20Rs%203%2C999.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20they%20offer%20specialised%20programmes%20such%20as%20the%20%3Cem%3ESolids%20Introduction%20Course%2C%20Breastfeeding%20Training%20Program%2C%20Baby%20Nutrition%20Program%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%3Cem%3E%20Sleep%20Training%20Program%3C%2Fem%3E.%20The%20%3Cem%3EHolistic%20Care%3C%2Fem%3E%20programme%20remains%20their%20bestseller%2C%20with%207%2C200%20paid%20customers%2C%20while%20over%20two%20lakh%20people%20have%20attended%20their%20free%20webinars.%20Their%20Instagram%20page%20has%20garnered%20over%20four%20and%20a%20half%20lakh%20followers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC3z-C9ZJqbo%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagra